1
00:00:01,300 --> 00:00:03,860
I have something to tell you.

2
00:00:03,860 --> 00:00:05,280
What?

3
00:00:08,360 --> 00:00:10,450
I have a crush on someone.

4
00:00:10,450 --> 00:00:12,860
♫ <i> Approaching is prohibited </i> ♫

5
00:00:12,860 --> 00:00:15,400
<i> [The Witch Store]</i>

6
00:00:15,400 --> 00:00:17,240
♫ <i> Until you apologize </i> ♫

7
00:00:17,240 --> 00:00:21,010
<i> [Episode 7] 
 [Timing Matters When it Comes to Love]</i>

8
00:00:21,010 --> 00:00:24,200
♫ <i> Approaching is prohibited </i> ♫

9
00:00:24,200 --> 00:00:26,020
Good morning!

10
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:29,020
What's wrong?

11
00:00:31,340 --> 00:00:35,020
What's up? You had fun yesterday on your date?

12
00:00:35,020 --> 00:00:37,360
They say you can't scratch your own back.

13
00:00:37,360 --> 00:00:39,219
Even as a witch, you must not be able to know things related to yourself.

14
00:00:39,220 --> 00:00:41,140
What are you talking about?

15
00:00:44,320 --> 00:00:46,880
<i>I have something to tell you.</i>

16
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:48,380
<i>What?</i>

17
00:00:51,380 --> 00:00:54,000
<i>I have a crush on someone.</i>

18
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:56,400
<i>Oh, really? Who?</i>

19
00:00:58,160 --> 00:01:00,340
<i>I like Youngji.</i>

20
00:01:00,340 --> 00:01:03,500
<i>What? Yoo Youngji?</i>

21
00:01:03,500 --> 00:01:05,220
<i>Yeah.</i>

22
00:01:05,220 --> 00:01:07,400
<i>Since when?</i>

23
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:09,740
<i>The day when she came to see us practice,</i>

24
00:01:09,740 --> 00:01:11,280
<i>was when I first saw her.</i>

25
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:13,520
<i>But, she...</i>

26
00:01:13,520 --> 00:01:16,120
<i>It is my first time having a crush on someone.</i>

27
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:18,200
<i>But you don't know her too well.</i>

28
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:19,480
<i>Exactly.</i>

29
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:21,300
<i>What should I do?</i>

30
00:01:21,300 --> 00:01:23,800
<i>You're the only one I can ask for help.</i>

31
00:01:23,800 --> 00:01:26,280
<i> I didn't see it coming.</i>

32
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:29,760
<i> Such situations happen more often than expected.</i>

33
00:01:32,240 --> 00:01:34,140
Why are you looking at me like that?

34
00:01:34,140 --> 00:01:37,060
What do you think of guys who are younger than you?

35
00:01:37,060 --> 00:01:39,420
What do you mean?

36
00:01:39,420 --> 00:01:42,060
Every guy on this planet is younger than me.

37
00:01:42,060 --> 00:01:45,780
Well, that's true.

38
00:01:45,780 --> 00:01:48,320
Oh, Yuho! Hi.

39
00:01:50,180 --> 00:01:53,020
Hey, hi.

40
00:01:54,220 --> 00:01:56,980
What's going on? Is something wrong?

41
00:01:56,980 --> 00:01:58,440
Of course.

42
00:01:58,440 --> 00:02:00,420
You had a date with Sungwoo yesterday.

43
00:02:00,420 --> 00:02:01,959
It wasn't a date!

44
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:04,400
Well, how did you know that?

45
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:06,620
I know everything.

46
00:02:06,620 --> 00:02:09,480
Well, Yuho must be struggling with his emotions.

47
00:02:09,480 --> 00:02:11,460
Why?

48
00:02:11,460 --> 00:02:15,360
Gosh. You're so clueless.

49
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:19,040
I knew you would be like this, so I prepared something specifically for you.

50
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,680
What is this?

51
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:27,360
This clock lets you know the perfect timing.

52
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:30,540
It's called Takimaksi in English.

53
00:02:30,540 --> 00:02:31,700
Takimak...

54
00:02:31,700 --> 00:02:33,940
Hey, you've just shortened a phrase into a word!

55
00:02:33,940 --> 00:02:37,580
Well, anyway. Take advantage of it. Take it.

56
00:02:38,340 --> 00:02:41,360
But, why are you giving it for free?

57
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,860
Are you giving weird stuff to me again?

58
00:02:42,860 --> 00:02:44,440
Weird?

59
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:46,580
You wouldn't be able to buy this anywhere else even if you wanted to.

60
00:02:46,580 --> 00:02:49,000
I think it is weird...

61
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:54,520
You must not know how to put on a watch.

62
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:56,440
It is weird.

63
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:58,720
Hey, girl. Look.

64
00:03:01,300 --> 00:03:03,600
Wow. Have you watched "Music Core"? 
 <i> (T/N: Corean TV show)</i>

65
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:06,980
- I love Chungha! 
 - Does Eunah know you're like this?

66
00:03:06,980 --> 00:03:09,260
Hey, love and fanboying are different.

67
00:03:09,260 --> 00:03:11,320
I know the difference.

68
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:13,440
Hey, will you go to the canteen?

69
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:16,620
That timing! We've just come from there.

70
00:03:16,620 --> 00:03:17,980
Oh, really?

71
00:03:17,980 --> 00:03:20,400
Next time. Sorry.

72
00:03:23,180 --> 00:03:25,240
<i> What's wrong with Yuho?</i>

73
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:27,520
<i> Did something really happen?</i>

74
00:03:32,020 --> 00:03:34,880
Complaints went up over the openness policy.

75
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:37,180
- Japan penetrated into the economy. 
 <i>- Why is he being so awkward?</i>

76
00:03:37,180 --> 00:03:41,780
- In 1882, the Im-O Military Revolt took place. 
 <i>- I don't know.</i>

77
00:03:43,500 --> 00:03:45,640
<i> Should I try using this once?</i>

78
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:48,880
<i> What does it mean? The perfect timing?</i>

79
00:03:50,020 --> 00:03:52,640
<i> Okay, I'll try using it.</i>

80
00:03:54,540 --> 00:03:56,560
The Byeolgigun Army was formed.

81
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:58,280
The old-fashioned army— Ah!

82
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:02,360
<i> What was that?</i>

83
00:04:08,200 --> 00:04:11,620
Youngji, would you switch seats with Yuho?

84
00:04:11,620 --> 00:04:14,000
Yes, Sir.

85
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:16,720
Why? Out of the blue?

86
00:04:17,460 --> 00:04:21,140
Just do it. Please.

87
00:04:21,140 --> 00:04:22,860
Please.

88
00:04:34,320 --> 00:04:35,920
I feel... good.

89
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:39,440
Okay, next. Move on.

90
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:48,620
Hi.

91
00:04:49,820 --> 00:04:51,320
Hi.

92
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:55,520
What's wrong with him?

93
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:58,240
I know, right?

94
00:04:58,240 --> 00:05:00,540
<i> Just wait and see.</i>

95
00:05:03,940 --> 00:05:06,220
How is it? It works, right?

96
00:05:06,220 --> 00:05:07,760
I don't trust you anymore.

97
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:10,220
Why? You're making me sad.

98
00:05:10,220 --> 00:05:12,340
That was too much.

99
00:05:12,340 --> 00:05:14,340
You are picky.

100
00:05:14,340 --> 00:05:16,960
Anyway, did you two work through the awkwardness?

101
00:05:16,960 --> 00:05:19,220
We feel more awkward thanks to your watch!

102
00:05:19,220 --> 00:05:20,960
You complain even when I'm helping you.

103
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:22,660
Give it back to me if you don't want it.

104
00:05:22,660 --> 00:05:25,080
I was planning on doing that anyway.

105
00:05:25,740 --> 00:05:27,460
What?

106
00:05:27,460 --> 00:05:30,060
<i> Ouch!</i>

107
00:05:30,060 --> 00:05:31,840
Hyungsuk, are you okay? What's wrong?

108
00:05:31,840 --> 00:05:33,160
I'm not sure.

109
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:35,140
What's going on?

110
00:05:35,140 --> 00:05:38,440
- I have a stomachache. 
 - Are you okay?

111
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:41,100
Sir. He's sick.

112
00:05:41,100 --> 00:05:43,520
I'll take him to the nurse's office.

113
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:46,580
Okay, please.

114
00:05:46,580 --> 00:05:51,580
Oh? Hyeji needs someone to play with now.

115
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:56,000
Then. Yuho, go be her partner.

116
00:06:00,260 --> 00:06:02,000
Thank you.

117
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,400
Sorry.

118
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:05,120
What?

119
00:06:08,620 --> 00:06:11,600
Hey, forget the nurse's office, I need to go to the bathroom.

120
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:15,020
Hey, it is okay. Calm down. You will be fine.

121
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:22,060
It's a little weird.

122
00:06:23,540 --> 00:06:25,980
I know, right. It is weird.

123
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:33,260
Do you want to go home together later?

124
00:06:33,260 --> 00:06:34,680
What?

125
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:37,080
Sure.

126
00:06:38,090 --> 00:06:43,090
♫ <i> The path I'm walking with you is awkward </i> ♫

127
00:06:43,090 --> 00:06:46,850
♫ <i> If tomorrow comes after a long night, </i> ♫

128
00:06:46,850 --> 00:06:48,860
It is cold, right?

129
00:06:48,860 --> 00:06:51,120
Yes, right.

130
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,890
♫ <i> Yeah</i> ♫

131
00:06:52,890 --> 00:06:56,460
♫ <i> It would be a shame to just part ways </i> ♫

132
00:06:56,460 --> 00:06:58,500
I think someone's calling you.

133
00:06:58,500 --> 00:07:00,640
Oh, excuse me.

134
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:04,480
Yes, dad?

135
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:07,520
Yes, I will be right there.

136
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:10,060
Why?

137
00:07:10,060 --> 00:07:13,460
He asked me to come help him. A part-timer is not available all of a sudden.

138
00:07:13,460 --> 00:07:15,120
Oh, you should hurry and go.

139
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:17,200
I should be going. Be careful going home.

140
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:19,300
Okay. See you tomorrow.

141
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:25,540
<i> What should I do?</i>

142
00:07:27,260 --> 00:07:29,620
<i> Do I have to use this?</i>

143
00:07:32,740 --> 00:07:36,140
<i> No. Let's not use it.</i>

144
00:07:42,540 --> 00:07:44,220
Hyeji!

145
00:07:46,340 --> 00:07:49,140
What are you doing this weekend?

146
00:07:49,140 --> 00:07:51,140
I'm not doing anything.

147
00:07:51,140 --> 00:07:54,160
Then, let's go have some fun.

148
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:55,540
Sure.

149
00:07:55,540 --> 00:07:57,420
Bye.

150
00:07:57,420 --> 00:08:00,260
♫ <i> Dozens of times a day </i> ♫

151
00:08:00,260 --> 00:08:06,340
<i> The problem I agonized over turned out to have a simple resolution.</i>

152
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:17,420
Hey, when will you be done?

153
00:08:17,420 --> 00:08:20,540
♫ <i> Like the sound of a bell in my head </i> ♫

154
00:08:20,540 --> 00:08:23,900
♫ <i> I understood what this was </i> ♫

155
00:08:23,900 --> 00:08:25,920
- Is it done? 
 - Yeah.

156
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:27,940
I think I am fine.

157
00:08:27,940 --> 00:08:29,640
Hey.

158
00:08:29,640 --> 00:08:31,640
Hey, please.

159
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:33,380
It's the fourth time.

160
00:08:33,380 --> 00:08:35,200
Sorry.

161
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,520
Oh, it is coming!

162
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:41,470
♫ <i> Would push me towards you </i> ♫
